        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>End Capitalization for Struggling Borrowers Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the capitalization of interest on a student loan balance after forbearance or certain deferment periods. Capitalization occurs when the interest accrued on a student loan during a period of deferment or forbearance is added to the principal amount of the loan at the expiration of such period. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
